     <div class=\"l-mega-nav__panel js-accordion-panel\">\n            <div>\n              <ul class=\"l-mega-nav__children\">\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/education/\">研修・育成</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/internship/\">インターンシップ</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/welfare/\">福利厚生</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <div class=\"l-mega-nav__accord js-accordion-trigger\">\n            <div class=\"c-ttl-primary\"><span class=\"ttl-en\">Recruit</span> <span class=\"ttl-jp\">リクルート</span></div><button class=\"trigger\" aria-label=\"メニューを開く\"></button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"l-mega-nav__panel js-accordion-panel\">\n            <div>\n              <ul class=\"l-mega-nav__children\">\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/requirement/\">募集要項</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/requirement/#faq\">よくある質問</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/meeting/\">会社説明会のご案内</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"l-mega__btn\"><a href=\"/recruit/entry/\" class=\"c-btn-circle\"><span class=\"txt u-uppercase\">Entry</span> <img class=\"arw\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/icons/arw_circle.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"18\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n    <div class=\"l-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"l-content\"><!-- main -->\n        <main class=\"l-main\">\n          <div class=\"l-page-hero\">\n            <div class=\"l-page-hero__head\">\n              <div class=\"l-inner\">\n                <h1 class=\"head-ttl\"><span class=\"ttl-en\">benefit</span> <span class=\"ttl-jp\">福利厚生</span></h1>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"l-page-hero__visual\">\n              <picture>\n                <source srcset=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/hero_visual_sp.webp\" media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                <source srcset=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/hero_visual_sp.jpg\" media=\"(max-width: 767px)\">\n                <source srcset=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/hero_visual.webp\" type=\"image/webp\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/hero_visual.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazy-none\" height=\"640\" width=\"2800\">\n              </picture>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"l-breadcrumbs l-page-bread\">\n            <div class=\"l-inner\">\n              <nav>\n                <ol vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"BreadcrumbList\">\n                  <li property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><a property=\"item\" typeof=\"WebPage\" title=\"採用情報TOP\" href=\"/recruit/\"><span property=\"name\">採用情報TOP</span></a>\n                    <meta property=\"position\" content=\"1\">\n                  </li>\n                  <li property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><span property=\"name\">福利厚生</span>\n                    <meta property=\"position\" content=\"2\">\n                  </li>\n                </ol>\n              </nav>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"l-page-cont\">\n            <section class=\"wel-lineup\">\n              <div class=\"l-inner\">\n                <h2 class=\"c-ttl-circle\">福利厚生</h2>\n                <ul class=\"wel-lineup__list l-sec-xl\">\n                  <li>\n                    <div><img class=\"info-icon\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/icon_holiday.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"80\" width=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\n                    <div>\n                      <h3 class=\"info-ttl\">休日休暇制度</h3>\n                      <ul class=\"c-list-dot -inline\">\n                        <li>土日祝休み（年4日土曜出勤あり）</li>\n                        <li>年間休日121日以上</li>\n                        <li>年末年始・夏期休暇</li>\n                        <li>年次有給休暇</li>\n                        <li>計画有給休暇</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                    <div><img class=\"info-icon\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/icon_child.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"80\" width=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\n                    <div>\n                      <h3 class=\"info-ttl\">子育て</h3>\n                      <ul class=\"c-list-dot -inline\">\n                        <li>産前産後休暇</li>\n                        <li>育児休業（男女ともに実績あり）</li>\n                        <li>短時間勤務制度</li>\n                        <li>看護休暇</li>\n                        <li>リモートワーク</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                    <div><img class=\"info-icon\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/icon_money.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"80\" width=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\n                    <div>\n                      <h3 class=\"info-ttl\">各種手当</h3>\n                      <ul class=\"c-list-dot -inline\">\n                        <li>家族手当</li>\n                        <li>住宅手当</li>\n                      </ul>\n                      <ul class=\"c-list-dot -inline\">\n                        <li>住宅補助手当</li>\n                        <li>通勤手当</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                    <div><img class=\"info-icon\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/icon_home.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"80\" width=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\n                    <div>\n                      <h3 class=\"info-ttl\">ライフプラン</h3>\n                      <ul class=\"c-list-dot -inline\">\n                        <li>確定拠出年金</li>\n                        <li>財形貯蓄</li>\n                        <li>各種祝金・弔慰金</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                    <div><img class=\"info-icon\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/welfare/icon_other.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"80\" width=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\n                    <div>\n                      <h3 class=\"info-ttl\">その他</h3>\n                      <ul class=\"c-list-dot -inline\">\n                        <li>表彰制度（永年勤続表彰、月間･年間MVP　他）</li>\n                        <li>社会保険完備</li>\n                        <li>介護休業</li>\n                        <li>クラブ活動</li>\n                        <li>定年65歳</li>\n                        <li>退職金制度</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                </ul>\n                <div class=\"wel-column l-sec-xl\" id=\"office\">\n                  <div class=\"wel-column__cont\">\n                    <div class=\"\">\n                      <h3 class=\"info-ttl\">オフィスが新しくなります</h3><a href=\"/column/?tags%5B%5D=workplace\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"c-btn-circle -wht l-lg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"リンクを新規タブで開きます\"><span class=\"txt\">みんなのワークプレイス</span><img class=\"arw\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/icons/blank.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"10\" width=\"10\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p class=\"u-mb-letter\">2026年、本社・物流センターが、より働きやすい空間に生まれ変わります。</p>\n                      <p>現在、若手社員を中心に、本社オフィスの働く空間を大リニューアルしています。プロジェクトの様子や、働く環境、若手社員の働く姿をこちらよりご覧ください。</p><a href=\"/column/?tags%5B%5D=workplace\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"c-btn-circle -wht l-sm u-mt-4\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"リンクを新規タブで開きます\"><span class=\"txt\">みんなのワークプレイス</span><img class=\"arw\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/icons/blank.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"10\" width=\"10\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"wel-column__bg\">\n                    <picture>\n                      <source srcset=\"/recruit/assets/images//welfare/c